content:
Bu belirteç başlıktaki "x-access-token" anahtar değerine eklenerek aşağıdaki GET istekleri gönderilebilir: Information of all tags defined in the system http://localhost:3000/api/auth/tags or http://localhost:3000/api/auth/tags/{id} Sample Result: [ { "id": 1, "tagname": "tag1", "kanal_id": 1, "polfreq": 3, "deviceaddress": "1", "variableaddress": "0", "variablesize": 4, "variabletype": 2, "islogging": 0, "privilegelevel": 0, "tagtype": 0, "schedulerindex": 0, "loggingfreq": 300, "loggingmethod": 6619250, "readright1": 0, "readright2": 0, "writeright1": 0, "writeright2": 0, "keywords": null, "enabled": 1, "description": null, "unitname": null, "protocolobjecttype": 0, "toption": 0, "logfilteroptions": "{
 "filtertype": 0,
 "refval1": null,
 "refval2": null
}
", "equipment": null, "measuredentity": null, "location": null, "formula": null, "modified": 0 }, … ] Kopyala Information of all alarms that defined in the system http://localhost:3000/api/auth/alarms or http://localhost:3000/api/auth/alarms/{id} Sample Result: [ { "id": 1, "alarm_name": "Alarm1", "alarm_desc": "NoDescription", "alarm_class": "General", "enabled": 1, "ackrequired": 0, "islogging": 0, "tag_id": 3, "alarm_type": 0, "alarm_level": 0, "comp_type": 1 }, … ] By using the "tag_id" value in this scheme, information about the tag that causes the alarm can be accessed from "api / auth / tags". Kopyala List of alarms that are instantly active in the system: http://localhost:3000/api/auth/active_alarms or http://localhost:3000/api/auth/active_alarms/{id} Sample Result: [ { "id": 4, "alarm_id": 1, "user_name": null, "dataval": 1, "currentstate": 1, "trigertime": 1537229311140, "acktime": -1, "recovtime": -1, "logtime": 1537229311140, "logdate": null, "mailsent": 0, "ackmessage": null }, … ] The details of the alarm can be accessed from "api / auth / alarms" by using the "alarm_id" value in this scheme. Kopyala Information of all channels defined in the system http://localhost:3000/api/auth/channels or http://localhost:3000/api/auth/channels/{id} Sample Result: [ { "id": 1, "channelname": "Channel1", "mediatype_id": 0, "sockettype_id": 0, "paritytype_id": 0, "protocoltype_id": 0, "serverport": 1080, "listenport": 1081, "serverip": "127.0.0.1", "filterip": "0.0.0.0", "comport": 11, "baudrate": 115200, "databit": 8, "stopbit": 1, "responseto": 6000, "connectionto": 6000, "frameto": 3000, "groupid": -1, "station": null, "enabled": 1, "logicpropath": null, "description": null, "modified": 0, "state": null }, … ] Kopyala Instantaneous values of labels defined in the system http://localhost:3000/api/auth/rt_values or http://localhost:3000/api/auth/rt_values/{id} Sample Result: [ { "id": 1, "tag_id": 3, "dataval": 1, "logtime": 1537229310000, "logdate": "2018-09-18T00:08:30.000Z" }, … ] Kopyala Updating the tag value in the system localhost:3000/api/auth/write_buffer
